(143, 'admin', 1, 'Main Admin', '', 'listing.updated', 'listing', 14, 'Mahachaiensis Betta', 'update', 'Updated listing #14 (Mahachaiensis Betta)', '{\"id\":\"14\",\"title\":\"Mahachaiensis Betta\",\"slug\":\"mah-260330-8836-6842\",\"species\":\"Betta splendens\",\"strain\":\"Mahachaiensis\",\"grade\":\"Normal\",\"short_description\":\"Wild bettas embody the pure, original lineage of the species—refined by nature, not human selection. Sensitive and deeply connected to their natural environment, they require calm, stable conditions and knowledgeable care.\\r\\nA true choice for collectors wh\",\"description\":\"Wild betta fish represent the original lineage of the species—untouched by selective breeding and deeply rooted in their natural heritage. Each individual carries the authenticity of its origin, shaped by generations in quiet, tannin-rich waters and delicate ecosystems that demand balance and stability.\\r\\nUnlike fancy bettas, wild bettas retain their instinctive sensitivity. They respond quickly to environmental changes, noise, and stress, requiring conditions that closely mirror their natural habitat. A calm setting, soft lighting, and consistent water parameters are not luxuries, but fundamental necessities for their survival and well-being.\\r\\nKeeping a wild betta is not a casual pursuit. It is a refined practice that calls for patience, discipline, and respect for nature. We strongly encourage all collectors to study their behavioral patterns and ecological needs in depth before making a selection.\\r\\nTo choose a wild betta is to honor its lineage—to preserve not only its physical form, but the spirit of the environment from which it came. This is more than ownership; it is stewardship of a living heritage.\",\"price\":\"39.00\",\"currency\":\"USD\",\"country\":\"Thailand\",\"city\":\"Chiang Mai\",\"status\":\"active\",\"featured\":\"1\",\"cover_image\":\"/uploads/listings/14/seller_14_20260330180927_7f47cfb469ce.jpg\",\"meta_title\":\"Buy Wild Betta Fish from Thailand | Rare & Natural Species\",\"meta_description\":\"Discover rare wild betta fish from Thailand. Authentic natural lineage, carefully selected and safely prepared for international collectors worldwide.\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-30 18:09:27\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-02 23:53:32\"}', '{\"id\":\"14\",\"title\":\"Mahachaiensis Betta\",\"slug\":\"mah-260330-8836-6842\",\"species\":\"Betta splendens\",\"strain\":\"Mahachaiensis\",\"grade\":\"Normal\",\"short_description\":\"Wild bettas embody the pure, original lineage of the species—refined by nature, not human selection. Sensitive and deeply connected to their natural environment, they require calm, stable conditions and knowledgeable care.\\r\\nA true choice for collectors wh\",\"description\":\"Wild betta fish represent the original lineage of the species—untouched by selective breeding and deeply rooted in their natural heritage. Each individual carries the authenticity of its origin, shaped by generations in quiet, tannin-rich waters and delicate ecosystems that demand balance and stability.\\r\\nUnlike fancy bettas, wild bettas retain their instinctive sensitivity. They respond quickly to environmental changes, noise, and stress, requiring conditions that closely mirror their natural habitat. A calm setting, soft lighting, and consistent water parameters are not luxuries, but fundamental necessities for their survival and well-being.\\r\\nKeeping a wild betta is not a casual pursuit. It is a refined practice that calls for patience, discipline, and respect for nature. We strongly encourage all collectors to study their behavioral patterns and ecological needs in depth before making a selection.\\r\\nTo choose a wild betta is to honor its lineage—to preserve not only its physical form, but the spirit of the environment from which it came. This is more than ownership; it is stewardship of a living heritage.\",\"price\":\"39.00\",\"currency\":\"USD\",\"country\":\"Thailand\",\"city\":\"Chiang Mai\",\"status\":\"active\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"cover_image\":\"/uploads/listings/14/seller_14_20260330180927_7f47cfb469ce.jpg\",\"meta_title\":\"Buy Wild Betta Fish from Thailand | Rare & Natural Species\",\"meta_description\":\"Discover rare wild betta fish from Thailand. Authentic natural lineage, carefully selected and safely prepared for international collectors worldwide.\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-30 18:09:27\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-03 00:22:32\"}', '1bb8a5bee9a397a36d177c2edb898209', '184.82.184.67', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '2026-04-03 00:22:32'),
